  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个AXI4 Lite主设备读监控器的结构图。核心组件是axil4_master_rd_mon，它要处理AXIL通道的读事务，最终输出64位的监控包到monbus。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "axil4_master_rd_mon",
        "AXIL_Channels",
        "Output",
        "MONBUS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。AXIL通道具体指哪些？是单独的AR和R通道，还是包含写通道？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AXIL_Channels",
        "AR",
        "R"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "只读操作，所以是AR Channel（读地址）和R Channel（读数据）。这两个通道要放在一个叫\"AXIL Master Channels\"的子图里。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AXIL_Channels",
        "AR",
        "R"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，AXIL Master Channels子图已创建，包含AR和R两个通道节点。现在axil4_master_rd_mon内部怎么划分？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AXIL_Channels",
        "AR",
        "R"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "监控器内部分两大部分：Monitor Base和Reporter。Base里放Transaction Tracker和Timeout Detection，Reporter里放Packet Generation。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "axil4_master_rd_mon",
        "Base",
        "TRANS",
        "TIMEOUT",
        "Reporter",
        "PKT"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下结构：axil4_master_rd_mon包含两个子图——Monitor Base（有TRANS和TIMEOUT）和Reporter（有PKT）。对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "axil4_master_rd_mon",
        "Base",
        "TRANS",
        "TIMEOUT",
        "Reporter",
        "PKT"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，但注意命名：Monitor Base和Reporter作为子图标签，内部节点分别是TRANS、TIMEOUT和PKT。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Base",
        "Reporter",
        "TRANS",
        "TIMEOUT",
        "PKT"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "监控器内部结构已画好。输出部分呢？你提到monbus。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "axil4_master_rd_mon",
        "Base",
        "Reporter",
        "TRANS",
        "TIMEOUT",
        "PKT"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "输出端单独放一个子图叫\"Monitor Bus Output\"，里面放MONBUS节点，标注为mon_* (64-bit packets)，表示64位监控包总线。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Output",
        "MONBUS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "Output子图和MONBUS节点已添加。现在来连数据流：AR和R都连到TRANS？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AR",
        "R",
        "TRANS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，AR Channel和R Channel都要接入Transaction Tracker，这样TRANS才能跟踪完整读事务。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AR",
        "R",
        "TRANS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "AR→TRANS和R→TRANS的连接已画好。接下来TRANS连TIMEOUT？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "TRANS",
        "TIMEOUT"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，TRANS把事务信息传给TIMEOUT做超时检测。检测到异常或正常完成后，TIMEOUT要触发PKT生成监控包。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "TRANS",
        "TIMEOUT",
        "PKT"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "TRANS→TIMEOUT和TIMEOUT→PKT的连接已完成。最后PKT输出到MONBUS？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PKT",
        "MONBUS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，PKT→MONBUS，这就是完整的监控数据流：从AXIL通道采集，经事务跟踪、超时检测，最后打包输出。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PKT",
        "MONBUS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 16,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "PKT→MONBUS已连接。整体结构完成了，我检查一下：AR、R → TRANS → TIMEOUT → PKT → MONBUS。流程正确吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AR",
        "R",
        "TRANS",
        "TIMEOUT",
        "PKT",
        "MONBUS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 17,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，TIMEOUT到PKT的箭头方向我刚才说反了逻辑。实际应该是TIMEOUT检测到超时事件后通知PKT生成包，但PKT也可以接收正常完成的事务。让我确认：TIMEOUT→PKT是对的，但PKT应该同时能接收TRANS的直接输入吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "TIMEOUT",
        "PKT",
        "TRANS"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 18,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "当前图里只有TIMEOUT→PKT，没有TRANS→PKT。需要加一条直接连线吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "TRANS",
        "TIMEOUT",
        "PKT"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 19,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "不需要，保持现状。TIMEOUT模块会聚合事务状态（正常完成或超时），统一输出给PKT。这样架构更清晰，Reporter只从Base的TIMEOUT接收触发。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "TIMEOUT",
        "PKT"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 20,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "了解。那子图标签的显示名称需要调整吗？比如\"axil4_master_rd_mon\"作为技术名称，内部用\"Monitor Base\"和\"Reporter\"作为可读标签？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "axil4_master_rd_mon",
        "Base",
        "Reporter"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 21,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，外层子图用技术名axil4_master_rd_mon，内层两个子图用功能名Monitor Base和Reporter。AXIL Master Channels和Monitor Bus Output也是功能描述性名称。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "axil4_master_rd_mon",
        "AXIL_Channels",
        "Base",
        "Reporter",
        "Output"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 22,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "所有标签已按规范设置。再确认节点标注：AR显示\"AR Channel\\n(Read Address)\"，R显示\"R Channel\\n(Read Data)\"，MONBUS显示\"mon_*\\n(64-bit packets)\"，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AR",
        "R",
        "MONBUS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 23,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "完全正确。TRANS、TIMEOUT、PKT保持简洁标签即可，它们的功能在子图上下文中已经明确。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "TRANS",
